metadata.name: Saturnus #1
metadata.description:
The embodiment of pure evil itself. He was born out of the accumulation of horrors that have been committed across the universe. He breathes fear and terror and feeds on the terrifying acts people do. 

He can sense evil throughout the universe and can warp instantly to where evil is present. A few have seen him but it is said that he will be present if an evil act is committed. He absorbs this evil and accumulates it to further grow his presence.

He has absorbed countless acts of evil, from which he has given life to several villainous minions, who in turn go and do his bidding, spreading fear, terror and destruction throughout the universe.

Throughout countless centuries he has grown to be the most terrifying being in existence.
